                        designed around your traffic, performance, and growth goals.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex flex-col min-[440px]:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
                        <a href="#comparsion" class="button-primary" data-i18n="customComponent.compareAllPlans"> Compare All Plans </a>
                        <a href="/contactUs" class="button-secondary flex items-center gap-2" data-i18n="customComponent.contactUs"> Contact Us </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>